# Local Agent (FastAPI + LangGraph + SQLite + Chroma)

This project provides a **local agent** for indexing and searching files using **FastAPI**, **LangGraph**, **SQLite**, and **ChromaDB**.  
It supports reading multiple document types and logs all search queries for auditing and analysis.

---

## Features
- ğŸ“‚ **Supported File Types**: `.pdf`, `.docx`, `.ppt`, `.pptx`, `.txt`, `.md`, `.csv`, `.xlsx`, `.json`, `.html`, `.xml`, `.rtf`, `.odt`, `.ods`, `.odp`.
- âš¡ **FastAPI** backend with auto-generated API docs at `/docs`.
- ğŸ” **ChromaDB** vector search with persistence at `./data/chroma`.
- ğŸ“ **SQLite logging** for users, queries, and hits (`./data/app.sqlite`).  
- ğŸ”— **LangGraph integration** for experimentation and dev workflows.
- âœ… **Test suite with pytest** covering file readers, search, and API endpoints.

